_sText: This is an enhanced version of my map fy_strongholds This map features: -Custom Skybox -Custom Soundscape -Cubemaps -Overview -Edited nav file with area names -Buyzones Also, all custom content has been embeded in the bsp for easy download from servers. The bsp filesize is 8.94MB. Also many thanks to Mini Madness for helping me out with the overview image. Have fun!
